text: Elizabeth or Elizaveta Petrovna (; ) reigned as Empress of Russia from 1741 until her death in 1762. She is one of the most popular Russian monarchs because of her decision not to execute a single person during her reign and her criticisms towards Prussian policies. ==References== Category:1709 births Category:1762 deaths Category:Emperors and Empresses of Russia
title: Elizabeth of Russia
